 \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Welshman_(newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.7714266515357984, \"rank\": 0.29629629629626636, \"text\": \"The Welshman\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Welshman_(newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Welshman_(newspaper)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his craft\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"his first time trials\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"open roads\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reward for a good ride then was a McDonald's on the way home, a routine he hopes to repeat this weekend.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reward\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"a good ride\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"a McDonald\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the way home\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a McDonald's by the hotel here,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a McDonald\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think on Sunday I will be hitting that.\\\"\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The custom was established when Tarling was a regular at the Ystwyth Cycling Club's weekly 10-mile time trial, and it continued until he was 16.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Ystwyth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ystwyth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Ystwyth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Ystwyth\"}, {\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999975434855674, \"rank\": 2.4565203793297656e-06, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Road_bicycle_racing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The custom\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We'd finish the 10 quite late and on the way back there was a Maccy D's,\\\" Tarling said.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"a Maccy D\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would be a lot skinnier if it wasn't for that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling will be up against some mighty competition this weekend.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"some mighty competition\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel is fresh from finishing third overall at the Tour de France, while Ganna is a two-time time trial world champion and the reigningItalianchampion.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.8718500088859438, \"rank\": 0.14698495431507375, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"Ganna\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-time time trial world champion\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"the reigningItalianchampion\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ganna and Remco and Wout have all done much more impressive stuff than I have,\\\" Tarling said.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ganna\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"Remco\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"Wout\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"much more impressive stuff\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Remco was flying in the Tour, Ganna won the time trial in the Giro, Wout's coming back (from injury) but he's still Wout, so my name flies under the radar quite nicely.\\\"\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Remco\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tour\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"Ganna\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the time trial\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"the Giro\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"Wout\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"the radar\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling does not yet have the same level of name recognition, but he has some serious chops.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the same level\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"name recognition\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"some serious chops\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, the year before he turned professional with theIneos Grenadiers, Tarling won nine of the 10 time trials he raced