537664664237856e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 32.4km course\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"the shortest and flattest course\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"modern Olympic history\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling would have liked a few more twists, knowing a technical circuit would play to his strengths, but - after doing a little over three laps in Wednesday's recon ride - he feels he knows where he can get the best out of himself.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"a few more twists\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"a technical circuit\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"his strengths\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"a little over three laps\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's recon ride\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even as others talk him up, the laid-back Tarling insisted he was not feeling the pressure.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"the laid-back Tarling\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No (pressure), because I can not control it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know I have done everything I can on my side so as long as I am happy with my ride I will be happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"my side\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"my ride\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling has already scored one psychological victory over Ganna.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"one psychological victory\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"Ganna\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ineos team-mates share a coach in former Italian time trial champion Dario Cioni, but Cioni will be in the team car of Tarling and not his compatriot this weekend.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}, {\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.48410148208382947, \"rank\": 0.7008965794910252, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Cioni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dario Cioni\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Cioni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Cioni\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"Cioni\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"the team car\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"not his compatriot\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If he wanted him, he should have booked him, eh?!\\\"\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"nou